{"tid":127310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心補習中介Hxxtutor","createTime":"2017-02-20T04:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T13:48:59.000Z","uid":74895,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"362430f0da1a1eba8b35ed91372d17f820bf872e","tid":127310,"uid":74895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"話說個補習中介 Hxxtutor 係我sem break既時候就比左兩單游水堂我教，兩單我都接左。<br />\n<br />\n第一單雖然拖左一拖但都有出糧。第二單上年九月做完就黎料。拖左兩個禮拜，我打電話去催，淨係講咩我幫你追追會計部，今個星期內應該會出。一路催一路拖，直到十二月已經無再聽過我電話。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一月個時，佢比左一單補習case問我接唔接，我同佢講左爭我好耐未出糧，不如你出返糧比我，我先再幫你地接啦。個中介即係扮哂野話，係咩？我幫你追下會計部下，跟住又係咁問我方唔方便接左單case先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我搵過勞工處，話呢啲係自僱形式，無辦法介入，叫我去民事索償。本身已經放棄當買個教訓，但今日，佢居然仲夠膽死又比單case我問我接唔接，今次真唔忍，決定係到呼籲大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n可能係我自己on9/唔好彩，但係小弟唔希望再有學生哥比呢啲垃圾中介呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edf205090d9040da6fc89014a17713124c1b242","tid":127310,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你推 佢係搵私人補習個d?"},{"pid":"b86669d04d8cdbbd8dce919d2ce398213081afaf","tid":127310,"uid":62110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"block 7左依間野好耐"},{"pid":"324975b9e14fdd86a203980a171dc032d1983803","tid":127310,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"放多啲資料上黎<br />\n最好係圖，如whatsapp記錄。<br />\n好快就有糧出架啦<br />\n<br />\n點解？香港人最撚憎人拖糧。"},{"pid":"7c94d2e0cd91f8e1e3675c5e7afe2d35f178a4e9","tid":127310,"uid":28846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a576011a77e4e85c7ff116512171f9983f48345d","tid":127310,"uid":29197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"呢間野條款幾西下<br />\n其他中介都係補左兩堂先入數 hxxtutor就要求補完第一堂 要入哂第一同第二堂既錢<br />\n結果我上完兩堂比家長炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話會45日內退番一半錢比我<br />\n佢個陣真係拖到45日先退比我<br />\n<br />\n再講多少少 接case前我一直同hxxtutor講 要6點先上得堂 佢拍哂心口話家長知架喇 ok架喇 冇問題<br />\n點知上完第一堂 老母問可唔可以5點開始<br />\n上完第二堂 個老母又問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後第二日hxxtutor通知我 個老母話唔補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家小心呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f002cd950de853153405b6890d32ab177c5e59","tid":127310,"uid":28846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9699c35141ab60ca3e23774bebc05e0070e9314c","tid":127310,"uid":24098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12877e1fb62c946c2c152095fcbf9d059d063385","tid":127310,"uid":74895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/124358_2db0f3adedef5dcec469121ee1c6f6d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F124358_2db0f3adedef5dcec469121ee1c6f6d7.jpg&h=27a05202&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/124358_e201906d9c7cb6095b44597d0c6d5bc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F124358_e201906d9c7cb6095b4459